WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.566 --> 00:00:02.800
In your eyes, I'm just a free meal ticket

2
00:00:02.800 --> 00:00:04.300
Does it matter if I ignore you?

3
00:00:04.600 --> 00:00:06.500
Ouch, disgusting.

4
00:00:06.666 --> 00:00:08.900
Sorry, I was wrong.

5
00:00:08.900 --> 00:00:10.466
It's not that I don't love you

6
00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:13.700
I just... I just want a better life.

7
00:00:14.100 --> 00:00:15.966
Didn't I give you a good life?

8
00:00:15.966 --> 00:00:17.500
I earn money outside to support my family

9
00:00:17.500 --> 00:00:19.700
I go home, I do my chores, I hold you in my hands.

10
00:00:19.700 --> 00:00:20.866
I hold you in my heart

11
00:00:20.866 --> 00:00:22.100
What did you do?

12
00:00:22.100 --> 00:00:24.166
But I should have been better than this.

13
00:00:24.200 --> 00:00:26.566
Wei Xin, if my brother hadn't died

14
00:00:26.566 --> 00:00:27.900
With his ability

15
00:00:27.933 --> 00:00:29.866
I can live a better life

16
00:00:32.600 --> 00:00:34.700
Trust me against your will

17
00:00:34.700 --> 00:00:35.666
I love you.

18
00:00:35.666 --> 00:00:38.066
But if you want to be with me

19
00:00:38.066 --> 00:00:40.700
You have to give me your best

20
00:00:40.700 --> 00:00:42.466
So what do you want me to do?

21
00:00:42.533 --> 00:00:44.600
Do you have the key to Jiang Lili's office bookcase?

22
00:00:44.600 --> 00:00:45.333
spoon

23
00:00:45.333 --> 00:00:48.066
You go and steal the design draft for his costume contest

24
00:00:48.366 --> 00:00:49.366
Are you crazy?

25
00:00:49.366 --> 00:00:51.566
That is the hard work of Brother An and his sister-in-law this month

26
00:00:51.566 --> 00:00:52.700
I see.

27
00:00:52.700 --> 00:00:54.933
But I contacted Rongmei's competitor.

28
00:00:54.933 --> 00:00:57.766
He said as long as we steal the design draft

29
00:00:57.766 --> 00:00:59.900
He can give us 100,000

30
00:01:00.900 --> 00:01:03.100
Big heart 100,000

31
00:01:03.100 --> 00:01:04.266
If this money

32
00:01:04.266 --> 00:01:06.300
We can buy our own house

33
00:01:07.300 --> 00:01:09.866
Weixin just this once

34
00:01:09.900 --> 00:01:11.166
We take the money and leave

35
00:01:11.166 --> 00:01:12.333
We can go to Guangcheng

36
00:01:12.333 --> 00:01:13.600
Go to Hujiang

37
00:01:13.600 --> 00:01:15.100
Have a life that belongs only to the two of us

38
00:01:15.100 --> 00:01:18.200
Is your life good?

39
00:01:23.933 --> 00:01:25.566
Brother An's sister-in-law is not good

40
00:01:25.566 --> 00:01:28.033
What was burned in the costume design draft?

